Description: volk is a meta-loader for Vulkan. It allows users to dynamically load
entrypoints required to use Vulkan without linking to the dynamic library or
statically linking Vulkan loader.
Revision is from `git merge-base JIRI_HEAD origin/upstream/vulkan-sdk-1.4.304`.
